---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Bodhic AI - Buy and Sell AI Agent Skills">
	<section class="hero">
		<h1>The Most Secure AI Agent Skill Marketplace</h1>
		<p>
			Discover, buy, and sell prompt artifacts designed for downstream AI agents. 
			Every skill is rigorously scanned for prompt injections and security threats.
		</p>
		<div class="auth-buttons" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
			<a href="/browse" class="btn btn-primary" style="font-size: 1.25rem; padding: 1rem 2rem;">Explore Skills</a>
			<a href="/sell" class="btn btn-secondary" style="font-size: 1.25rem; padding: 1rem 2rem;">Start Selling</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section>
		<h2>Why Choose Bodhic AI?</h2>
		<div class="grid">
			<div class="glass-card">
				<h3><span class="highlight">01.</span> Advanced Security</h3>
				<p>Our Tier-1 synchronous scanner detects prompt injections, secrets, and excessive agency claims before a skill even goes live.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="glass-card">
				<h3><span class="highlight">02.</span> Localized Pricing</h3>
				<p>We automatically adjust prices and payment methods based on your country, supporting multiple global providers.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="glass-card">
				<h3><span class="highlight">03.</span> Multi-Provider Payouts</h3>
				<p>Sellers get paid in their preferred local currency via Stripe, Razorpay, Paystack, Mercado Pago, and PayPal.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
